&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Experiment:&lt;/strong&gt; Run tests and iterate on large datasets to constantly move the needle on performance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bridge Platforms:&lt;/strong&gt; Build pipelines and services that connect on-device signals to algorithmic decision-making.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;End-to-End Ownership:&lt;/strong&gt; Take features from an initial idea to full production with measurable user impact.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
