&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cross-Functional Collaboration:&lt;/strong&gt; Work closely with engineering and product teams to translate research breakthroughs into production systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What We’re Looking For&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
