&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;CV Fundamentals:&lt;/strong&gt; A deep understanding of Computer Vision principles and practical experience applying them to real data.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;End-to-End Training:&lt;/strong&gt; Experience managing the full training pipeline, including data curation, augmentation, evaluation, and iteration.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Coding Proficiency:&lt;/strong&gt; Strong programming skills and the ability to bridge the gap between research code and production-ready solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
