&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Meet Oasis&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Introducing Oasis, the newest innovation from Mixtiles! We&#39;re on a mission to show the world how the right lighting can utterly transform any space, elevating its warmth, beauty, and overall ambiance. It&#39;s about more than just visibility; it&#39;s about setting a mood, creating an atmosphere, and infusing life into every corner, making your environment not only look, but also feel infinitely more inviting and alive.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Oasis aims to bring great lighting within everyone&#39;s reach. We are starting our most ambitious journey yet, and determined to make Oasis a familiar name in homes everywhere.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For those inspired by the fusion of design and technology, and who dream of pioneering in spaces where aesthetics meet innovation, Oasis is your calling.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Join us in revolutionizing lighting.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’re applying for&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’re looking for a Head of Engineering for Oasis, Mixtiles&#39; newest venture into the smart lighting world. Ideal for a tech visionary passionate about IoT, ready to shape our direction from the ground up. In this key role, you&#39;ll work closely with the Oasis GM and our management team, navigating the intricacies of integrating software, hardware, and firmware to craft user experiences that seem effortlessly magical. Your expertise will not only define the technical backbone of Oasis but also lay the groundwork for its success in homes nationwide. This is your chance to be at the heart of innovation, making a real-world impact and shaping the future of great lighting.&amp;nbsp;&lt;

