&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’re applying for&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a detail-oriented Quality Control Contractor with a passion for plants and strong technical abilities to support our grow facility through weekly plant inspections and documentation. This part-time role requires approximately 8 hours of work per week and is ideal for someone who enjoys hands-on work in plant nurseries and greenhouses.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;In this role you&#39;ll be pivotal in shaping the future of home design&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Here&#39;s what you&#39;ll do:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Document new batches of plants, including taking photos and maintaining detailed records.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct inspections of plant stock to identify signs of pests, diseases, or physical damage.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Measure plants to ensure growth and size consistency according to company standards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with the QC Supervisor on additional quality control tasks as needed to maintain plant quality in line with company specifications.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Requirements:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Independent transportation to the facility - near Frederick, Maryland, United States.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong technical skills for accurate measurement and keen observation to identify plant defects and issues.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Horticulture or houseplant knowledge and experience are a plus.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A BS or BA in a scientific field is a plus.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Competent using digital tools, including forms and other software, for documentation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Schedule:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;One full day of on-site work per week, approximately 8 hours.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Compensation:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Competitive pay based on experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you are passionate about plant care and have the skills to maintain high quality standards in a greenhouse environment, we&#39;d love to hear from you!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

